=== Expected Outcomes

If the hypothesis is supported, this study would:
    - Provide first direct evidence that crashes deplete measurable biological reserves
    - Validate crash prevention as disease-modifying intervention
    - Identify which RPI components are most crash-sensitive
    - Inform clinical recommendations about crash prevention intensity
